[girl 1] Hey, nerd!

1027
00:52:49,375 --> 00:52:51,291
[Jeremy] No. Hey, hey, hey!
That's not fair!

1028
00:52:51,375 --> 00:52:52,875
[girl 1] Come on! Go, go!

1029
