[Tommy grunting]

1040
00:53:19,458 --> 00:53:21,583
Alright, next question.

1041
00:53:21,666 --> 00:53:24,250
-Uh…
-["Sweet Jane" playing over stereo]

1042
00:53:24,333 --> 00:53:27,291
What about you and your sister?
You guys ever get along?

1043
00:53:27,791 --> 00:53:29,958
Thought these were supposed to be
easy questions.

