But I wouldn't expect
a Sunnyvaler to understand.

1080
00:55:17,833 --> 00:55:19,458
No, maybe you're right.

1081
00:55:20,125 --> 00:55:23,833
But, uh… being the heir apparent
isn't always easy either.

1082
00:55:24,708 --> 00:55:25,791
Before he died,

1083
00:55:26,458 --> 00:55:29,416
my dad loaded me up with all this,

1084
00:55:29,500 --> 00:55:31,458
you know, "You're my legacy,

1085
00:55:31,541 --> 00:55:34,083
the future of the family
depends on you" shit.

1086
00:55:35,291 --> 00:55:39,916
You know, he just dropped
this huge burden in my lap and…

1087
00:55:40,000 --> 00:55:41,875
I dunno, what if I don't want that?

1088
00:55:41,958 --> 00:55:43,958
What if that's not who I want to be?

1089
00:55:44,041 --> 00:55:49,541
What if I want to be the kid
who likes spiders and Stephen King and--

1090
00:55:49,625 --> 00:55:51,625
And the weird girl from Shadyside?

1091
00:55:54,458 --> 00:55:55,375
Yeah.

1092
00:55:55,458 --> 00:55:57,625
[sentimental music fades out]

1093
00:55:57,708 --> 00:55:59,291
The weird girl from Shadyside.

1094
00:55:59,375 --> 00:56:01,958
-["Sweet Jane" continues over radio]
-But, uh…

1095
00:56:02,833 --> 00:56:05,041
I guess there's nothing I can do about it.

1096
00:56:05,541 --> 00:56:06,500
Why not?

1097
00:56:06,583 --> 00:56:09,750
♪ Some people
They like to go out dancing ♪

1098
00:56:09,833 --> 00:56:13,375
Yeah, you were right. Can we, uh…
Can we go back to the easy questions?

1099
00:56:14,750 --> 00:56:15,791
OK.

1100
00:56:18,583 --> 00:56:19,583
Um…

1101
00:56:20,375 --> 00:56:21,583
How about…

1102
00:56:21,666 --> 00:56:23,666
♪ Everything is just dirt… ♪

1103
00:56:23,750 --> 00:56:27,833
-Would you ever kiss the weird girl?
-♪ But anyone who ever had a heart ♪

1104
00:56:27,916 --> 00:56:32,333
♪ Oh, they wouldn't turn around
And break it ♪

1105
