-[crowd screaming]
-[boy] He's dead!

1111
00:56:45,916 --> 00:56:48,208
-[boy] Jeremy's dead!
-[man] No, you guys! OK? Hey!

1112
00:56:48,291 --> 00:56:51,541
We're done. Everyone get back.
Hey, no! Color War's done! Alright?

1113
00:56:51,625 --> 00:56:54,083
-Get out of here! Get out!
-[Ziggy gasps]

1114
00:56:54,166 --> 00:56:56,125
[man] Let's go! Get out! Let's go!

1115
00:56:56,833 --> 00:57:00,625
Alright, it branches off again here.
Just stay left.

1116
00:57:00,708 --> 00:57:02,041
[Alice gasping]

1117
00:57:02,125 --> 00:57:05,041
I cannot believe this is working.

1118
00:57:05,916 --> 00:57:08,708
It's taking too long.
He could be back at camp already.

1119
00:57:10,958 --> 00:57:12,416
If you have to kill him…

1120
00:57:12,916 --> 00:57:13,916
could you?

1121
00:57:14,708 --> 00:57:17,916
Earlier, when Mary attacked, I just…

1122
00:57:20,166 --> 00:57:22,125
I froze. I couldn't do anything.

1123
00:57:25,875 --> 00:57:29,958
So, no, I… I couldn't kill anyone,
much less Tommy.

1124
00:57:31,208 --> 00:57:33,875
Well, good news. I would happily kill him.

1125
00:57:34,500 --> 00:57:38,708
God, even now, after everything,
you're… you're still a jerk.

1126
00:57:38,791 --> 00:57:42,541
[Alice] OK, I'm sorry. I just…
I never got what you saw in him.

1127
00:57:42,625 --> 00:57:45,791
And that was before
the witch possessed him.

1128
00:57:46,708 --> 00:57:47,666
Tommy… [sighs]

1129
00:57:48,708 --> 00:57:50,083
Tommy was sweet.

1130
00:57:51,041 --> 00:57:52,583
He made me feel like

1131
00:57:53,791 --> 00:57:55,916
everything was going to be OK.

1132
00:57:56,708 --> 00:57:58,208
I loved him.

1133
00:57:58,291 --> 00:57:59,708
I really did.

1134
00:57:59,791 --> 00:58:01,208
[Alice] I loved Arnie too.

1135
00:58:02,208 --> 00:58:05,083
I loved that gross, high little shit.
[inhales deeply]

1136
00:58:06,458 --> 00:58:08,458
[deep rumbling]

1137
00:58:08,541 --> 00:58:09,666
Do you hear that?

1138
00:58:11,000 --> 00:58:13,000
There's this space here up ahead.

1139
00:58:13,833 --> 00:58:16,083
All roads lead here.

1140
00:58:18,791 --> 00:58:20,583
Is there any other way around?

1141
00:58:20,666 --> 00:58:23,833
[rumbling continues]

1142
00:58:23,916 --> 00:58:26,625
[flies buzzing]

1143
00:58:26,708 --> 00:58:28,833
[breathing heavily]

1144
00:58:31,791 --> 00:58:32,916
[Alice] What the hell?

1145
00:58:33,000 --> 00:58:34,750
Flies? What is this stuff?

1146
00:58:34,833 --> 00:58:36,000
It's everywhere.

1147
00:58:38,958 --> 00:58:39,916
Cindy?

1148
00:58:41,916 --> 00:58:43,083
What is that?

1149
00:58:43,750 --> 00:58:45,083
[beating]

1150
00:58:45,833 --> 00:58:48,208
-[beating]
-[flies buzzing]

1151
00:58:48,875 --> 00:58:49,875
[beating]

1152
00:58:49,958 --> 00:58:51,291
Let's get out of here.

1153
00:58:51,833 --> 00:58:53,291
[beating]

1154
00:58:55,250 --> 00:58:58,166
-[whispering voice] Alice…
-[beating]

1155
00:59:00,500 --> 00:59:02,291
[whispering voice] Alice…

1156
00:59:11,458 --> 00:59:12,416
[Cindy] Alice!

1157
00:59:12,500 --> 00:59:15,041
[Alice screaming]

1158
00:59:16,083 --> 00:59:17,208
[Cindy] Alice?

1159
00:59:17,291 --> 00:59:19,666
[Alice yelling]

1160
00:59:19,750 --> 00:59:21,500
[high-pitched scream]

1161
00:59:21,583 --> 00:59:24,375
[panting]

1162
00:59:25,416 --> 00:59:26,916
[high-pitched scream]

1163
00:59:28,916 --> 00:59:30,166
[yelling]

1164
00:59:30,250 --> 00:59:31,458
[screams]

1165
00:59:31,541 --> 00:59:34,583
[ominous music intensifies]

1166
00:59:35,708 --> 00:59:37,583
-[bone breaks]
-[screams in pain]

1167
00:59:38,875 --> 00:59:40,750
[whimpering]

1168
00:59:40,833 --> 00:59:42,041
[school bell ringing]

1169
00:59:42,125 --> 00:59:45,666
Let's go! This is not part of the game!
Go, guys! Go, go!

1170
00:59:45,750 --> 00:59:47,916
Five, seven, eight, ten,

1171
00:59:48,000 --> 00:59:49,875
fifteen, eighteen…

1172
00:59:49,958 --> 00:59:52,791
[kids screaming]

1173
00:59:52,875 --> 00:59:56,541
-[Nick] Stay calm! Everything's alright!
-How many?

1174
00:59:56,625 --> 00:59:58,916
-Twenty-three.
-That's 30 missing at least.

1175
00:59:59,000 --> 01:00:01,833
-Where's Cindy, Kurt, Joan?
-I don't know. I haven't seen them.

1176
01:00:01,916 --> 01:00:03,375
Or Tommy or anyone.

1177
01:00:03,458 --> 01:00:06,000
-[boy] The lights are coming on!
-Maybe they're looking for us.

1178
01:00:06,083 --> 01:00:08,500
-[Nick] It's dead.
-We have to go. We have to warn people.

1179
01:00:08,583 --> 01:00:11,875
-I'm sure they heard the bell. Hey!
-My sister, she's still out there!

1180
01:00:11,958 --> 01:00:14,250
The same sister you've hated
since you were a baby?

1181
01:00:14,333 --> 01:00:16,375
Look, I'm sorry.

1182
01:00:16,458 --> 01:00:19,125
I didn't mean it. Me and Gary will go.

1183
01:00:19,625 --> 01:00:21,166
-What?
-Just please stay here.

1184
01:00:21,250 --> 01:00:23,458
-I can't sit here!
-I'm not letting you get hurt!

1185
01:00:24,791 --> 01:00:26,583
-[girl] What the hell?
-[Nick] OK?

1186
01:00:27,208 --> 01:00:30,125
Please, let me do my job.

1187
01:00:30,208 --> 01:00:33,250
I'm gonna find your sister.
Just stay here. OK?

1188
01:00:33,333 --> 01:00:35,166
[indistinct chatter]

1189
01:00:35,250 --> 01:00:38,291
-You.
-Hey, you realize that's a camper, right?

1190
01:00:38,375 --> 01:00:41,166
Look, you make for cabin one.
I'll head to nine.

1191
01:00:41,250 --> 01:00:44,458
-What if the killer's still out there?
-That's the whole point, Gary.

1192
01:00:45,625 --> 01:00:49,625
Hey, everybody! Stay here! OK? OK.

1193
01:00:49,708 --> 01:00:52,458
[ominous music playing]

1194
01:00:52,541 --> 01:00:53,375
Hey!

1195
01:00:54,500 --> 01:00:57,416
-Where is she, witch?
-You kill her like you killed Jeremy?

1196
01:00:57,500 --> 01:00:59,083
-What are you talking about?
-Sheila!

1197
01:00:59,166 --> 01:01:00,250
Where the fuck is Sheila?

1198
01:01:02,041 --> 01:01:02,875
Shit!

1199
