Joan!

1205
01:01:25,791 --> 01:01:27,000
Fuck.

1206
01:01:27,083 --> 01:01:29,250
Where the fuck is everyone?

1207
01:01:29,333 --> 01:01:33,041
-["Slow Ride" playing]
-[Joan moaning]

1208
01:01:34,291 --> 01:01:36,416
Stay put, big boy.

1209
01:01:36,500 --> 01:01:38,458
[Joan moaning]

1210
01:01:38,541 --> 01:01:40,791
-[Joan screaming]
-[Kurt] Oh, yeah. Oh!

1211
01:01:40,875 --> 01:01:42,541
♪ Take it easy… ♪

1212
01:01:42,625 --> 01:01:45,125
[both moaning]

1213
01:01:47,625 --> 01:01:48,666
[Kurt exhales deeply]

1214
01:01:49,250 --> 01:01:52,625
You tell anyone about this,
and you're dead.

1215
01:01:53,791 --> 01:01:55,541
-You hear me?
-Yeah.

1216
01:01:57,666 --> 01:01:59,375
♪ Take it easy… ♪

1217
01:01:59,458 --> 01:02:02,083
Just admit that Shadysiders do it better.

1218
01:02:02,750 --> 01:02:04,375
[Kurt] I ain't admitting shit.

1219
01:02:04,958 --> 01:02:06,166
He knows.

1220
01:02:10,916 --> 01:02:12,958
♪ Move to the music… ♪

1221
01:02:13,750 --> 01:02:15,625
[humming]

1222
01:02:20,125 --> 01:02:21,958
[sighs] Yes.

1223
01:02:26,166 --> 01:02:27,375
[high-pitched shrill]

1224
01:02:30,208 --> 01:02:34,125
[Kurt] Joan, I can smell that shit
from here! Put it out!

1225
01:02:34,208 --> 01:02:37,041
You know, you Sunnyvalers
are really missing out.

1226
01:02:38,541 --> 01:02:40,041
This shit, like, really…

1227
01:02:41,125 --> 01:02:43,250
opens up your mind.

1228
01:02:43,333 --> 01:02:44,416
[Kurt] Put it out!

1229
01:02:45,500 --> 01:02:49,000
[ominous music playing]

1230
01:02:51,041 --> 01:02:53,958
[music continues over stereo]

1231
01:02:57,291 --> 01:02:59,083
[ominous music playing]

1232
01:03:11,541 --> 01:03:12,875
[door creaks]

1233
