[screams]

1237
01:03:28,083 --> 01:03:30,333
[grunting]

1238
01:03:33,500 --> 01:03:36,458
[Alice grunting in pain]

1239
01:03:36,541 --> 01:03:37,541
[Cindy] Alice!

1240
01:03:37,625 --> 01:03:38,583
Jesus!

1241
01:03:38,666 --> 01:03:40,000
[Alice whimpering]

1242
01:03:40,083 --> 01:03:41,458
I was there, in the past.

1243
01:03:41,541 --> 01:03:43,958
-You're OK.
-I saw the… the killers.

1244
01:03:44,041 --> 01:03:46,250
They killed so many and you're next.

1245
01:03:46,333 --> 01:03:47,875
You're fucking next!

1246
01:03:47,958 --> 01:03:50,916
No, no, no, no.
That's not true. I'm right here.

1247
01:03:51,000 --> 01:03:52,333
The witch did this.

1248
01:03:53,166 --> 01:03:56,458
She did all of this. She put a curse
on Shadyside. Mary was right.

1249
01:03:56,541 --> 01:03:57,500
I know.

1250
01:03:58,000 --> 01:04:00,208
The cave was alive, Alice.

1251
01:04:01,791 --> 01:04:03,125
Tylenol can't do that.

1252
01:04:03,208 --> 01:04:04,500
[giggles, screams in pain]

1253
01:04:05,000 --> 01:04:06,375
[gasping]

1254
01:04:08,791 --> 01:04:10,000
[Cindy] You were right.

1255
01:04:11,791 --> 01:04:12,791
I am a snitch.

1256
01:04:13,916 --> 01:04:16,625
The day after we stole
Mr. Evans's JVC player,

1257
01:04:17,500 --> 01:04:19,375
Harold Hines saw me with it.

1258
01:04:19,458 --> 01:04:21,000
Fucking Harold Hines.

1259
01:04:21,083 --> 01:04:23,833
[pained screaming]

1260
01:04:23,916 --> 01:04:27,500
Next thing I know,
I'm in the Principal's office,

1261
01:04:27,583 --> 01:04:29,333
and my dad can't come in

1262
01:04:29,416 --> 01:04:33,208
because he just ran off with some girl
not much older than I am now.

1263
01:04:33,291 --> 01:04:38,250
And my mom, well, she was having
a few drinks at O'Connell's.

1264
01:04:38,333 --> 01:04:39,708
And I knew then…

1265
01:04:41,083 --> 01:04:43,250
I wasn't different
from the other Shadysiders.

1266
01:04:44,458 --> 01:04:45,750
I was cursed.

1267
01:04:47,333 --> 01:04:49,375
I told myself if I was perfect,

1268
01:04:49,458 --> 01:04:51,291
if I did everything right,

1269
01:04:51,375 --> 01:04:52,916
I could beat it.

1270
01:04:53,666 --> 01:04:55,041
I snitched on you,

1271
01:04:55,833 --> 01:04:57,250
I got new friends, I…

1272
01:04:58,708 --> 01:05:00,500
started dressing like this.

1273
01:05:05,833 --> 01:05:07,333
I dated sweet Tommy.

1274
01:05:09,125 --> 01:05:10,708
I avoided you,

1275
01:05:10,791 --> 01:05:12,916
but I couldn't avoid Ziggy.

1276
01:05:16,083 --> 01:05:19,125
Because she was always there,
reminding me of the truth.

1277
01:05:19,208 --> 01:05:21,291
That this town, this place… [sniffs]

1278
01:05:23,166 --> 01:05:24,166
…was cursed.

1279
01:05:26,083 --> 01:05:27,583
And so were we.

1280
01:05:28,833 --> 01:05:29,875
Now I know.

1281
01:05:30,625 --> 01:05:31,833
She was right…

1282
01:05:34,750 --> 01:05:35,916
all this time.

1283
01:05:37,583 --> 01:05:39,416
[Alice screams]

1284
01:05:39,500 --> 01:05:41,125
[Cindy] I've been a bad sister.

1285
01:05:42,916 --> 01:05:44,250
I've been a bad friend.

1286
01:05:46,833 --> 01:05:47,833
I should've just…

1287
01:05:48,708 --> 01:05:51,750
skipped class, partied, had sex, had fun.

1288
01:05:51,833 --> 01:05:53,541
[Alice] I hate to break it to you,

1289
01:05:54,291 --> 01:05:55,500
but the fun…

1290
01:05:58,708 --> 01:06:00,958
it's not any more real
than your polo shirt.

1291
01:06:01,458 --> 01:06:02,833
There's a reason I wear these.

1292
01:06:04,708 --> 01:06:06,916
And it's not just because they're awesome.

1293
01:06:14,625 --> 01:06:17,666
[sighs shakily] We all have our ways
to deal with Shadyside.

1294
01:06:23,791 --> 01:06:25,458
[hesitantly] What? What is it?

1295
01:06:25,541 --> 01:06:27,583
[breathing heavily]

1296
01:06:27,666 --> 01:06:28,541
This.

1297
01:06:28,625 --> 01:06:31,791
This moss, it stained my shirt.
The outhouse!

1298
01:06:36,791 --> 01:06:39,250
This stuff is all over the outhouse.

1299
01:06:41,583 --> 01:06:42,708
Camp.

1300
01:06:44,833 --> 01:06:46,250
It means we're close.

1301
01:06:47,291 --> 01:06:50,208
Everyone, listen up! The game is over!

1302
01:06:50,791 --> 01:06:53,791
Get back to the Mess Hall
or I'll dock you a victory point!

1303
01:06:54,833 --> 01:06:56,166
[twig breaks]

1304
01:06:57,625 --> 01:06:59,250
Claire! Freddy! Jesus!

1305
01:06:59,958 --> 01:07:02,500
Get to the Mess Hall! Come on! Go!

1306
01:07:09,250 --> 01:07:10,750
Everyone, the game is over!

1307
01:07:11,666 --> 01:07:13,291
[Nick] Get back to the Mess Hall!

1308
01:07:13,875 --> 01:07:15,083
Was that Counselor Goode?

1309
01:07:15,166 --> 01:07:16,791
Hey! I said no talking!

1310
01:07:17,541 --> 01:07:20,000
-He said the game was over!
-No talking, dweeb!

1311
01:07:20,666 --> 01:07:23,500
Just stay put.
I'll check with Counselor Goode.

1312
01:07:23,583 --> 01:07:26,375
Hey, we need… that.

1313
01:07:26,458 --> 01:07:27,416
[boy] Hold on.

1314
01:07:38,000 --> 01:07:39,375
Maybe we should just leave.

1315
01:07:42,000 --> 01:07:42,875
[boy] Shit!

1316
01:07:49,208 --> 01:07:50,666
[ominous music playing]

1317
01:07:51,250 --> 01:07:52,416
Counselor Tommy?

1318
01:07:53,916 --> 01:07:56,541
[campers screaming]

1319
01:07:56,625 --> 01:08:02,708
-[ax thudding against bodies]
-[knife drawn]

1320
01:08:03,750 --> 01:08:05,916
[owl hooting]

1321
01:08:07,250 --> 01:08:11,000
[breathing heavily]

1322
01:08:12,458 --> 01:08:13,666
Oh shit!

1323
01:08:21,708 --> 01:08:22,958
Sheila?

1324
01:08:23,958 --> 01:08:25,500
Sheila, are you still in here?

1325
01:08:26,208 --> 01:08:27,333
Sheila?

1326
01:08:30,083 --> 01:08:32,125
-You bitch!
-[Ziggy screams]

1327
01:08:32,208 --> 01:08:34,375
Sheila! Listen to me!

1328
01:08:38,083 --> 01:08:39,250
Do you smell that?

1329
01:08:40,083 --> 01:08:41,083
[Alice] Ugh.

1330
01:08:41,750 --> 01:08:43,166
It smells like shit.

1331
01:08:47,166 --> 01:08:50,125
-Is that toilet paper?
-[Cindy] It's the outhouse. It's gotta be.

1332
01:08:54,166 --> 01:08:56,583
-[Alice] Holy shit.
-[Cindy] There it is. Look.

1333
01:08:58,458 --> 01:08:59,458
[Sheila] Bitch!

1334
01:09:00,250 --> 01:09:02,833
[Sheila and Ziggy grunting, screaming]

1335
01:09:05,125 --> 01:09:07,083
I'm trying to help you! There's a killer--

1336
01:09:08,750 --> 01:09:09,833
[Ziggy] Oh shit!

1337
01:09:09,916 --> 01:09:12,041
-I heard shouting. What's going--?
-[Ziggy gasps]

1338
01:09:12,750 --> 01:09:14,916
-What's going on in here?
-Is everyone OK?

1339
01:09:15,000 --> 01:09:16,958
No! Everyone's headed back
to the Mess Hall.

1340
01:09:17,041 --> 01:09:18,041
Where's Nick?

1341
01:09:18,708 --> 01:09:21,666
[muffled screaming]
Help! Help! We're down here! Help!

1342
01:09:22,250 --> 01:09:23,166
Do you hear that?

1343
01:09:23,250 --> 01:09:26,166
[muffled shouting]

1344
01:09:26,250 --> 01:09:27,375
[muffled] Hello?

1345
01:09:28,333 --> 01:09:30,333
-[muffled shouting] Down here!
-Please help us!

1346
01:09:30,416 --> 01:09:33,416
-Please, help us!
-Get us out of here!

1347
01:09:33,500 --> 01:09:36,000
-[now louder] Hey! Hello!
-Help us!

1348
01:09:36,083 --> 01:09:37,708
[Cindy] Will you please help us?

1349
01:09:37,791 --> 01:09:38,750
Cindy?

1350
01:09:38,833 --> 01:09:41,000
Ziggy? Oh my God!

1351
01:09:41,083 --> 01:09:43,291
-What are you doing down there?
-[Cindy] It's…

1352
01:09:43,375 --> 01:09:44,625
[Cindy panting]

1353
01:09:44,708 --> 01:09:47,250
[Cindy] It's kind of a long story.
Are you OK?

1354
01:09:47,333 --> 01:09:48,500
Yeah, hold on a second.

1355
01:09:48,583 --> 01:09:50,750
Ziggy, are you OK?

1356
01:09:50,833 --> 01:09:52,458
[muffled] Are you OK?

1357
01:09:54,125 --> 01:09:55,208
What is going on?

1358
01:09:55,291 --> 01:09:57,625
-My sister's in the toilet.
-What?

1359
01:09:57,708 --> 01:09:58,875
Gary! Just help me!

1360
01:09:59,458 --> 01:10:02,833
Come on! Go! Back to the Mess Hall,
you hear me? Let's go!

1361
01:10:02,916 --> 01:10:05,875
[menacing music playing]

1362
01:10:09,500 --> 01:10:11,416
If anyone's in there, the game's over!

1363
01:10:24,333 --> 01:10:25,333
Oh God.

1364
01:10:25,833 --> 01:10:28,458
[menacing music intensifies]

1365
01:10:35,000 --> 01:10:36,083
Oh shit!

1366
01:10:37,000 --> 01:10:38,958
[retching]

1367
01:10:39,041 --> 01:10:40,125
[spits]

1368
01:10:42,291 --> 01:10:43,666
[pants]

1369
01:10:43,750 --> 01:10:47,250
Nick! I came out of the bathroom,
she was just dead, man! I swear to God!

1370
01:10:49,333 --> 01:10:50,500
Jesus, man.

1371
01:10:51,666 --> 01:10:53,083
Did you do this?

1372
01:10:53,791 --> 01:10:56,958
-Listen, there's a fucking killer.
-What?

1373
01:10:57,041 --> 01:10:59,958
We have to get the others out of here.
Get back to the Mess Hall.

1374
01:11:00,041 --> 01:11:02,166
In 15 minutes, ring the bell.

1375
01:11:02,250 --> 01:11:03,916
Ring the bell, that's the signal.

1376
01:11:04,000 --> 01:11:06,625
Get them on the bus,
get them out of here. Alright?

1377
01:11:06,708 --> 01:11:07,875
You hear me?

1378
01:11:07,958 --> 01:11:09,625
Just go! Go, Kurt!

1379
01:11:09,708 --> 01:11:11,958
[menacing music playing]

1380
01:11:19,958 --> 01:11:22,875
-[Ziggy] Get on! We're pulling you up!
-[laughing] Yes!

1381
01:11:23,666 --> 01:11:26,250
-[Alice] Dude, oh my God.
-Pull it. You first.

1382
01:11:30,375 --> 01:11:31,666
[rope creaks]

1383
01:11:33,125 --> 01:11:34,458
Now!

1384
01:11:35,458 --> 01:11:39,583
[both grunting]

1385
01:11:42,375 --> 01:11:44,458
[Alice grunting]

1386
01:11:47,666 --> 01:11:49,250
[grunting]

1387
01:11:56,333 --> 01:11:57,291
[Ziggy] Keep pulling!

1388
01:11:58,083 --> 01:11:59,791
[door creaks open]

1389
01:11:59,875 --> 01:12:01,875
Tommy! Tommy, what are you doi…

1390
01:12:02,625 --> 01:12:04,000
[screams]

1391
01:12:04,083 --> 01:12:06,250
[screaming]

1392
01:12:08,833 --> 01:12:11,166
[Cindy and Alice screaming]

1393
01:12:11,250 --> 01:12:13,375
[screaming]

1394
01:12:16,750 --> 01:12:17,958
[panting]

1395
01:12:20,166 --> 01:12:21,500
[Cindy] Ziggy!

1396
01:12:21,583 --> 01:12:24,583
-[Cindy] Ziggy!
-[Alice] Get him off!

1397
01:12:24,666 --> 01:12:27,041
-Ziggy! Ziggy!
-Get him off me!

1398
01:12:28,000 --> 01:12:30,833
-[Alice] Get him off! Get him off!
-Ziggy!

1399
01:12:32,875 --> 01:12:33,791
[Ziggy gasps]

1400
01:12:33,875 --> 01:12:34,916
What are you doing?

1401
01:12:35,000 --> 01:12:36,708
-He's here!
-Come on!

1402
01:12:46,375 --> 01:12:49,416
-Did we lose him?
-Yeah, I think so. Are you OK? You hurt?

1403
01:12:51,250 --> 01:12:52,916
It's not my blood. It's Gary's.

1404
01:12:54,041 --> 01:12:58,416
-And yours?
-Um… Sean, Jesse, Rod, Stacey.

1405
01:12:58,500 --> 01:13:01,291
Shadysiders. It's the curse.

1406
01:13:01,375 --> 01:13:03,291
No, it's, uh, it's just some psycho.

1407
01:13:03,375 --> 01:13:06,208
No, no, it's not some psycho. It's Tommy.

1408
01:13:06,291 --> 01:13:09,916
My sister's perfect, virgin,
boring boyfriend Tommy.

1409
01:13:10,000 --> 01:13:11,000
She did this.

1410
01:13:11,625 --> 01:13:13,625
-[Nick] Cindy?
-The witch!

1411
01:13:14,583 --> 01:13:16,000
That's not real, Ziggy.

1412
01:13:16,083 --> 01:13:18,791
Exactly what Sunnyvaler would say.
I thought you were different.

1413
01:13:18,875 --> 01:13:19,708
[bell ringing]

1414
01:13:19,791 --> 01:13:21,875
They're getting on the bus. We have to go!

1415
01:13:21,958 --> 01:13:26,083
-I can't! My sister is still out there!
-Ziggy, I've let a lot of people die.

1416
01:13:26,166 --> 01:13:29,083
-Nick, this isn't your fault.
-Not you! I'm not letting you die.

1417
01:13:30,083 --> 01:13:31,708
Because, uh… yeah!

1418
01:13:31,791 --> 01:13:34,041
I do like the weirdo from Shadyside.

1419
01:13:34,125 --> 01:13:35,791
Maybe once we get out of this,

1420
01:13:35,875 --> 01:13:38,541
we could, uh…
we could start a book club or something.

1421
01:13:38,625 --> 01:13:42,541
Maybe… I dunno, Stephen King's new one
is supposed to be good, I hear.

1422
01:13:43,041 --> 01:13:45,791
I'm done with King.
Judy Blume for me from now on.

1423
01:13:46,875 --> 01:13:49,041
Yeah, Judy Blume sounds, uh…
sounds perfect.

1424
01:13:49,958 --> 01:13:52,291
You believe me, right? About the curse?

1425
01:13:53,083 --> 01:13:55,375
Yeah, of course. I am different.

1426
01:13:56,500 --> 01:13:58,875
Now, come on. We gotta get out of here.

1427
01:13:58,958 --> 01:14:01,541
We'll call the cops.
Your sister's gonna be alright.

1428
01:14:01,625 --> 01:14:03,416
First, we gotta get on that bus.

1429
01:14:03,500 --> 01:14:05,208
[banging on door]

1430
01:14:18,625 --> 01:14:22,458
-[breathing heavily]
-[fly buzzing]

1431
01:14:29,791 --> 01:14:31,416
[exhales deeply]

1432
01:14:36,125 --> 01:14:38,541
[snake hissing]

1433
01:14:41,000 --> 01:14:42,541
[snake hissing]

1434
01:14:53,750 --> 01:14:54,750
[Tommy grunts]

1435
01:14:59,125 --> 01:15:01,666
[menacing music intensifies]

1436
01:15:15,625 --> 01:15:18,041
[snake hissing]

1437
01:15:21,375 --> 01:15:25,833
[menacing music crescendos]

1438
01:15:29,625 --> 01:15:31,208
[snake hissing]

1439
01:15:34,166 --> 01:15:35,958
-[Ziggy screams]
-Ziggy!

1440
01:15:36,625 --> 01:15:38,250
[Ziggy screaming]

1441
01:15:41,916 --> 01:15:43,250
[Nick grunts in pain]

1442
01:15:43,333 --> 01:15:44,458
[Nick] Run.

1443
01:15:44,541 --> 01:15:45,583
Aaah! Run!

1444
01:15:47,291 --> 01:15:48,666
Run!

1445
01:15:50,333 --> 01:15:52,750
[menacing music crescendos]

1446
01:15:55,458 --> 01:15:57,250
Ziggy! [panting]

1447
01:15:58,000 --> 01:15:59,291
Ziggy!

1448
01:16:02,958 --> 01:16:04,833
We have to find another way out.

1449
01:16:05,333 --> 01:16:06,708
What if there's not?

1450
01:16:06,791 --> 01:16:08,500
[Alice] No, no, there's gotta be.

1451
01:16:08,583 --> 01:16:11,250
We're at the outhouse. We're at camp.

1452
01:16:11,833 --> 01:16:14,208
Come on, get the diary. We're too close.

1453
01:16:17,833 --> 01:16:19,958
OK, these… these tunnels.

1454
01:16:21,166 --> 01:16:23,125
The witch, she made them, right?

1455
01:16:23,208 --> 01:16:24,208
Yeah?

1456
01:16:25,041 --> 01:16:29,291
And, "She emerged by the Meeting House,

1457
01:16:30,041 --> 01:16:31,625
one hand severed lost forever."

1458
01:16:31,708 --> 01:16:34,500
The Meeting House, which is now…

1459
01:16:36,541 --> 01:16:37,666
The Mess Hall.

1460
01:16:38,500 --> 01:16:39,833
There's gotta be another way out.

1461
01:16:40,875 --> 01:16:42,416
Oh God!

1462
01:16:42,500 --> 01:16:43,791
Come on!

1463
01:16:43,875 --> 01:16:45,916
-I'm just gonna slow you down.
-Alice!

1464
01:16:46,000 --> 01:16:49,208
No, it's fine. I'll catch up.
You gotta save your sister.

1465
01:16:49,291 --> 01:16:50,125
No…

1466
01:16:50,208 --> 01:16:51,083
Go!

1467
01:16:59,375 --> 01:17:02,833
Kurt! Will! Anybody!

1468
01:17:04,291 --> 01:17:05,208
[gasps]

1469
01:17:10,791 --> 01:17:14,250
[breathing heavily]

1470
01:17:28,250 --> 01:17:29,541
[Alice grunts]

1471
01:17:39,833 --> 01:17:41,125
"Blood will fall…"

1472
01:17:48,291 --> 01:17:50,708
"When she is near, blood will fall."

1473
01:17:51,916 --> 01:17:55,333
"Her hand laid to rest
atop Satan's stone."

1474
01:18:02,750 --> 01:18:03,916
Satan's stone…

1475
01:18:06,541 --> 01:18:08,208
[grunting]

1476
01:18:10,541 --> 01:18:13,750
[grunting]

1477
01:18:24,500 --> 01:18:26,500
[Cindy gasping]

1478
01:18:28,125 --> 01:18:29,125
[gasps]

1479
01:18:37,791 --> 01:18:40,208
[groaning]

1480
01:18:41,916 --> 01:18:43,166
[chuckles]

1481
01:18:44,458 --> 01:18:46,500
-Hello?
-[metal rattling]

1482
01:18:46,583 --> 01:18:49,166
Can anyone hear me? Hello?

1483
01:18:49,750 --> 01:18:52,333
[Cindy grunting]

1484
01:18:52,416 --> 01:18:53,416
Hello?

1485
01:18:54,500 --> 01:18:56,708
Can anyone hear me? Hello!

1486
01:18:56,791 --> 01:18:58,750
[ominous music playing]

1487
01:19:08,541 --> 01:19:09,666
[gasps]

1488
01:19:13,041 --> 01:19:16,791
["Carry On Wayward Son"
playing over loudspeaker]

1489
01:19:16,875 --> 01:19:19,083
♪ There'll be peace when you are done… ♪

1490
01:19:19,166 --> 01:19:23,541
Hey! Hey, I'm over here! Help!

1491
01:19:25,375 --> 01:19:28,125
♪ Don't you cry no more… ♪

1492
01:19:39,541 --> 01:19:41,000
[screaming] Help!

1493
01:19:46,208 --> 01:19:50,083
-[grate banging]
-[Cindy grunting]

1494
01:20:00,125 --> 01:20:01,875
[knocking on door]

1495
01:20:10,333 --> 01:20:12,291
[banging on grate]

1496
01:20:18,166 --> 01:20:19,458
[Tommy grunting]

1497
01:20:22,291 --> 01:20:26,000
♪ Lay your weary head to rest ♪

1498
01:20:26,791 --> 01:20:29,125
♪ Don't you cry no more ♪

1499
01:20:39,833 --> 01:20:43,333
♪ Masquerading as a man with a reason ♪

1500
01:20:43,416 --> 01:20:44,833
-♪ My charade-- ♪
-[music stops]

1501
01:20:44,916 --> 01:20:46,583
-[gasps]
-[floorboard creaks]

1502
01:20:47,458 --> 01:20:48,916
[Ziggy screams]

1503
01:20:50,833 --> 01:20:52,333
[Ziggy screams]

1504
01:20:52,416 --> 01:20:53,416
Ziggy!

1505
01:20:53,916 --> 01:20:54,916
Ziggy!

1506
01:20:55,416 --> 01:20:57,208
[banging on grate]

1507
01:20:57,291 --> 01:20:58,708
[Tommy grunts]

1508
01:20:58,791 --> 01:20:59,666
[Ziggy] No!

1509
01:21:00,666 --> 01:21:02,083
[Ziggy screams, choking]

1510
01:21:05,250 --> 01:21:07,000
[choking]

1511
01:21:08,208 --> 01:21:09,750
[Ziggy screams]

1512
01:21:11,750 --> 01:21:14,000
[gasping]

1513
01:21:15,041 --> 01:21:17,291
[Ziggy screaming]

1514
01:21:17,375 --> 01:21:20,958
[Tommy grunting]

1515
01:21:22,041 --> 01:21:24,000
[Ziggy gasping]

1516
01:21:24,083 --> 01:21:25,416
[Ziggy screams]

